name: Aline Abboud
description:
A request of @lemke.

Aline Abboud is a German journalist and TV host.

500-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images (all of them kindly provided by @lemke himself) with my usual settings.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
